desc: Target Level 4 or lower "Battlewasp" monsters in your GY, up to the number of monsters your opponent controls; Special Summon them. You can only activate 1 "Summoning Swarm" per turn. desc: If a monster(s) on the field is destroyed by battle or an opponent's card effect: You can Special Summon this card from your hand. Metal Skeleton" once per turn.

name: Traptrix Sera
desc:
1 non-Link "Traptrix" monster
This Link Summoned card is unaffected by Trap effects. You can only use each of the following effects of "Traptrix Sera" once per turn, and not during the Damage Step.
● If a Normal Trap Card is activated: You can Special Summon 1 "Traptrix" monster from your Deck with a different name than the cards you control.

desc: You can discard 1 other "HERO" monster; Special Summon this card from your hand.
